{"word":"Daniel","slug":"daniel","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Daniel</b> <a href=\"#/H1840\">H1840</a><br/><a href=\"#/H1841\">H1841</a> <br/> 1. A Jewish captive, called Belteshazzar<br/> - Educated at king's court<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=27&chapter=1'>Dan 1</a> <br/> - Interprets visions<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=27&chapter=2'>Dan 2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=27&chapter=4'>Dan 4</a> <br/> - Promotion and executive authority of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=27&chapter=2&verse=49'>Dan 2:49</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=27&chapter=5&verse=11'>Dan 5:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=27&chapter=5&verse=29'>Dan 5:29</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=27&chapter=6&verse=2'>Dan 6:2</a> <br/> - Conspiracy against, cast into the lions' den<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=27&chapter=6'>Dan 6</a> <br/> - Prophecies of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=27&chapter=4&verse=9'>Dan 4:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=27&chapter=7'>Dan 7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=24&verse=15'>Mat 24:15</a> <br/> - Abstinence of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=27&chapter=1&verse=16'>Dan 1:16</a> <br/> - Wisdom of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=27&chapter=1&verse=17'>Dan 1:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=28&verse=3'>Eze 28:3</a> <br/> - Devoutness of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=27&chapter=2&verse=18'>Dan 2:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=27&chapter=6'>Dan 6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=27&chapter=9'>Dan 9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=27&chapter=12&verse=13'>Dan 12:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=14&verse=14'>Eze 14:14</a> <br/> - Courage and fidelity of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=27&chapter=4&verse=27'>Dan 4:27</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=27&chapter=5&verse=23'>Dan 5:23</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=27&chapter=6&verse=23'>Dan 6:23</a> <br/> - Worshiped by Nebuchadnezzar<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=27&chapter=2&verse=6'>Dan 2:6</a> <br/> 2. David's son. Called Chileab<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=3&verse=3'>2Sa 3:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=3&verse=1'>1Ch 3:1</a><br/> 3. A descendant of Ithamar, and a companion of Ezra<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=15&chapter=8&verse=2'>Ezr 8:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=10&verse=6'>Neh 10:6</a>"}]}